00:00:27.570 --> 00:00:31.370
in the context of an enterprise,
security planning requires that you have

00:00:31.370 --> 00:00:35.700
some sort of a security policy,
what exactly is a security policy.

00:00:35.700 --> 00:00:39.450
A security policy really sort
of at the high level articulate,

00:00:39.450 --> 00:00:41.850
what are the security objectives are?

00:00:41.850 --> 00:00:43.470
What is that want to?

00:00:43.470 --> 00:00:45.270
What goals do we have?

00:00:45.270 --> 00:00:48.752
We want to maintain confidentiality.

00:00:48.752 --> 00:00:51.970
We want to make sure that
sensitive is not disclosed

00:00:51.970 --> 00:00:54.060
