00:00:54.060 --> 00:00:56.620
We want our systems to be available.

00:00:56.620 --> 00:00:58.900
We don't want our data to be corrupted.

00:00:58.900 --> 00:01:01.340
We don't want sensitive
data to get into the hands.

00:01:01.340 --> 00:01:03.430
We want to be legally compliant or
whatever.

00:01:03.430 --> 00:01:07.220
Cause you can think of all the kind of
security objectives somebody might have.

00:01:07.220 --> 00:01:10.920
