of course, is good for its employees.

00:01:32.470 --> 00:01:36.620
So that's the articulation of
the outlined reasons why we want to

00:01:36.620 --> 00:01:39.020
have the kind of policy that we do.

00:01:39.020 --> 00:01:44.090
So the policy is really what you
should do and what should not be done.

